This paper presents a neural solver for arithmetic expression calculation problem using deep neural networks and reinforcement learning. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), neural networks (cs.NE), and computer vision (cs.CV).
